{"tid":419746,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有村架純有望蟬聯紅白司儀","createTime":"2017-09-30T17:41:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T18:29:46.000Z","uid":14730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c100469ec244aec5995cf2deb590394e56a2f37f","tid":419746,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T17:41:36.000Z","msg":"最近主演NHK電視台晨早劇《雛鳥》的有村架純，憑新劇人氣再度急升，首播以來收視不俗，連續多個星期收視率維持在20%以上，加上劇集即將於本月底播出結局，或可把有村架純的人氣推上高峰。<br />\n<br />\n將於除夕舉行的重頭節目「紅白歌唱大賽」，近日盛傳有村架純繼去年擔任紅組司儀後，今年有望冧莊，而白組司儀則是男團嵐的成員大野智或櫻井翔。<br />\n<br />\n據報NHK依照慣例，將於11月公布表演陣容，本月開始跟各演出單位洽談。早前宣布將於明年9月退出樂壇的安室奈美惠，日媒指以她跟NHK交情深厚，加上有傳電視台斥資3億日圓（約2100萬港元）製作費兼出場費來利誘她，故安室最後一次亮相「紅白」的機會甚高。另有報道指，安室的恩師小室哲哉有意為她製作「畢業歌」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2x512UL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2x512UL&d=azkxzIsve6Kou3%2FBdsdzYk4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=a770ecc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2x512UL</a>"},{"pid":"0140c93982d4a9469592e8849e0eaee3165f3b01","tid":419746,"uid":110112,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T18:06:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://livedoor.blogimg.jp/booq/imgs/c/d/cdd39aab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flivedoor.blogimg.jp%2Fbooq%2Fimgs%2Fc%2Fd%2Fcdd39aab.jpg&h=3ba4a50c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c324ef897c7792a3f2314b50f44935f844980bbf","tid":419746,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T18:29:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://livedoor.blogimg.jp/booq/imgs/c/d/cdd39aab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flivedoor.blogimg.jp%2Fbooq%2Fimgs%2Fc%2Fd%2Fcdd39aab.jpg&h=3ba4a50c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}